                    "text":"The date in the header is UTC/GMT. I don't know what you mean by &quot;my java app read it as&quot;. Do you really mean &quot;my java app displays it as&quot;? If you display it in your local time zone, it's going to be 9:54. Unless you do something special, it's always going to be displayed in your local time zone."
